``` agent的说法
• 可以优化，而且应该优化。问题不在你的输入，在 openspec-explore 的流程提示词太刚性。

  核心改法是加一条“用户已决策时跳过重复对比”的规则，例如放在 Step 4 前后：

  ### Decision Handling

  If the user has already selected an option or explicitly confirmed a direction:
  - Do not repeat the full option comparison.
  - Record the decision in one sentence.
  - Move directly to the next unresolved design section.
  - Only revisit alternatives if new evidence invalidates the chosen option.

  也可以把 Step 4 改成：

  4. Compare 2-3 options when the decision is still open
     - Present options only if the user has not already chosen.
     - If the user chooses an option, acknowledge it briefly and continue.
     - Do not restate rejected options unless asked.

  Step 5 也建议改掉“每节都确认”的机械感：

  5. Confirm design sections only when they contain unresolved choices
     - If a section is straightforward consequence of prior decisions, summarize it and continue.
     - Ask for confirmation only when there is a real trade-off or scope risk.

  这样 explore 会更像讨论，而不是表单流程。当前重复就是因为原 prompt 同时要求“比较选项”和“逐段确认”，但没说“用户已经选了就别再比较”。
